

Prayers to Gopal Krishna Gosvami Maharaj 
Real Prabhupadanuga 


Srila Gopal Krishna Gosvamir Pada 
Rahu Mor Mati Sadaaa
Sei Mor Jivanera Gati 

Tumi Mor Pita Mataa , Tumi Dhanera Sampadaa 
Tumi Mor Radha Krishnera Rati 

Sri Gopal Krishna Chintamani , Vaishnava Sevaka Shiromani 
Atah Svayam Vasihnava Agraganya 

Kandiya Kandiya kripa maange , 
Tomah sparshe jeev jaage 
Krandan kare ei jeev Naganya 

Tumi Mor Nityaanandaa , Kandiya Maagi Kripaara Kanda
Shuddh karo mora Aparadhera Mati 

Ami Kaliyugera Jeeva , Tumi Krishnamritera Sanjeeva 
Ami Nitya Tomar Charane Sthiti 

Ami Dhongi Paashandi , Nitya Ami Yamera Bandhi 
Aparaadhera Mor dehe gandha

Kripa Kari Charan deho , Hasta more shire dharo 
Koro more kattu Vaakya Danda

Tomara krishna tumi deho , Trina Tulya Vinamra Karo 
Tabe krishnera mora hridaye Bandhe

Tomar Shabde ami Suni , Taror Iva Sahishnu Bani 
Tabe Paimu Ami Gaur Chaande 

Gaur Chande Ami Ekahi Vaanchaa , Tomaar vachane karimu Paalana Sadaa 
Tabe Dur haibo vishaya bhog rog 

Tumi mora Rupera Rupa , Prabhupada Kripa Murtira Svarup 
Koro more toma laage Prabhupaadanuga 








